data.description: Move in ready beautiful condo with 3 spacious bedrooms and 2 bathrooms in gorgeous Colonial Crossing neighborhood. A lot of beautiful modern touches and finishes throughout the condo. Open floor plan with vaulted ceiling and corner gas fireplace in the living room. Colonial Crossing offers many amenities including a fitness center, pool and clubhouse, jogging trails, dog park, playground, lake with lighted fountain and gazebo. This home is located near Ft. Eustis and has easy access to I-64. You are also just a short distance to Busch Gardens, Great Wolf Lodge, Historical Williamsburg and Jamestown. Schedule your showing today!
